{"tid":1709940,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"全民抛垃圾出馬路，千祈唔好咁做","createTime":"2019-11-12T04:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T07:34:02.000Z","uid":238340,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"94e55c63ce2ecccadf1aee088626bd0ec3fd7950","tid":1709940,"uid":238340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:38:58.000Z","msg":"大家  千祈吾好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">有人同我講</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非</span>，每次發夢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">汽水，咖啡</span></span><br />\n大家飲完既<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">水樽</span></span>，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">裝滿水</span></span>，帶出街<br />\n每人帶最少兩支<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k96pZhk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk96pZhk.jpg&h=d78daf1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最好係方形</span></span>，唔容易碌來碌去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBPvapk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBPvapk.jpg&h=96e410c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDR11v8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDR11v8.jpg&h=d58092a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拋出馬路</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無風險，放喺地下路邊，踢出馬路<br />\n數量多，自然會<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">變路障</span></span><br />\n雖然冇咁重，量多，都會好麻煩，執死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n緊急情況下，唔可以俾市民<br />\n用來淋熄催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">邊個咁戇居拎黎飲，通常係藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">重新一次，千祈唔好咁做</span></span><br />\n比人話亂拋垃圾，就吾好<br />\n我反對大家咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302e6173bff5d3a28e8cb5e01f24fe2ddac6d92f","tid":1709940,"uid":3865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"11.13 晨曦行動 繼續三罷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1709918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1709918</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cefb2ec48892f9316ec2d9bc267856b5af9832f3","tid":1709940,"uid":238340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9ab7ea1faab8e5c55595c7942a09d351cc6080d","tid":1709940,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:07:47.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"b079d4d7c21b1a7c502696939d9d6615c006defa","tid":1709940,"uid":238340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:38:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"111d82fbb4fe890a103afcd4e54de1c92e178d56","tid":1709940,"uid":310982,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:59:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d457fe3a7c09787932b73cd0d328c4cebee9210","tid":1709940,"uid":238340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:49:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cd73124b21e6faf11ee174bd2d01044e4ccc6785","tid":1709940,"uid":238340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:55:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a74cea3417b1e0fb5d08038144352503f2e25a2a","tid":1709940,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:21:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">繼續啊繼續啊繼續啊繼續到落實五大訴求煲底相見啊屌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民同我早早早早早起，繼續無限三罷，癱瘓交通，攬炒經濟！</span